These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, azure, light-blue
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, argentine, pakistani
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, lacrosse
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, train
1. the argentine is the person who likes azure##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the pakistani##1
5. the spanish is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is the pakistani##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Color      | light-blue  | white       | azure   |
| Nationality          | pakistani | spanish | argentine |
| Sport         | basketball  | lacrosse | rowing    |
| Transport   | train | trike       | helicopter      |

