.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, weightlifting
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, hip-hop, techno
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, paramedic, analyst
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster, family
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the paramedic##1
4. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Sport          | snowboarding      | rowing  | weightlifting        |
| Music-Genre         | techno | hip-hop | reggae |
| Job   | mechanic | paramedic | analyst       |
| Movie-Genre           | family     | disaster     | scientific      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, cabbage, spinach
House: craftsman, ranch-style, farmhouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, ebony, red
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, november
1. the farmhouse house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who likes red is in the middle##1
5. the person who likes amber is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Food      | cabbage    | pomegranate        | spinach |
| House           | ranch-style    | farmhouse | craftsman    |
| Color   | amber | red             | ebony  |
| Birthday     | november     | july                | october  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, rat, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, skiing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, june, january
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, lemonade
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the owner of the goat is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Pet          | rat    | mouse  | goat      |
| Sport           | skiing    | badminton | parkour |
| Birthday   | january   | june  | november     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | soy-milk    | lemonade      |

