.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: canasta, snooker, chess
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, scooter
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, cola
House: colonial, townhouse, cape-cod
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the townhouse house is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person driving the scooter is the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
5. the colonial house is the person playing canasta##1
6. the person drinking cola is the person driving the bus##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game         | chess | canasta     | snooker   |
| Transport           | scooter       | quad-bike   | bus     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | mirinda | cola |
| House           | cape-cod      | colonial         | townhouse  |

