.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, chess
House: tower, gothic-revival, townhouse
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, doctor, software-developer
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
3. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the software-developer##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Game          | scrabble | mah-jongg       | chess |
| House   | townhouse     | tower       | gothic-revival   |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks      | gardening       | reading     |
| Job         | engineer   | doctor | software-developer  |

