.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, ritmeester, havana
3 different games are played: monopoly, domino, go
3 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, cat
City: prague, colone, liverpool
1. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Cigar          | havana       | ritmeester         | aristoff   |
| Game           | monopoly | go | domino |
| Pet   | lizard     | pony        | cat        |
| City   | colone      | prague           | liverpool        |

