.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, apricot, green
There 3 different types of food: mango, pepper, cucumber
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, poppy
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, polish
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the person who growspoppy is the polish##1
3. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
6. the colombian is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Color         | apricot   | green | lavender |
| Food   | mango | cucumber         | pepper       |
| Flower           | balloon-flower      | poppy      | bellflower         |
| Nationality     | spanish      | polish         | colombian          |

