.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, pink, black
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, coffee
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, biathlon
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, indian
1. the indian is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes pink is the nigerian##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes black is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Color       | pink            | grey      | black  |
| Beverage         | coffee | almond-milk | fanta |
| Sport         | handball               | biathlon | lacrosse |
| Nationality   | nigerian             | indian       | indonesian      |

