There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, pink, brown
1. the victorian house is the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Flower           | daisy | dahlia         | zinnia |
| House   | modern      | victorian | farmhouse     |
| Beverage   | cola   | mirinda       | hot-chocolate     |
| Color           | brown    | pink         | blue        |

