3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| City           | liverpool | marseilles | hamburg |
| Cigar   | dannemann        | oliveros       | baccarat     |
| Game   | canasta     | whist         | mah-jongg     |
| Beverage     | milk | mirinda          | iced-tea      |

