3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person eating pear##1
4. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to london##1
5. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Game         | billiard | canasta | snooker   |
| City           | colone     | marseilles    | london   |
| Food   | spinach         | pear    | broccoli   |
| Flower         | iris       | sunflower | dahlia |

