The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, sailing, skiing
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the game-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday      | december      | november    | july    |
| Cigar          | game         | oliveros    | havana   |
| Pet           | lizard | horse | turtle |
