3. the person eating peas is the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the person eating tomato##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Food      | tomato         | peas     | cabbage     |
| Pet           | guinea-pig        | snake | pony |
| Flower   | amaryllis        | lily   | zinnia    |
| Color         | light-blue | grey   | ivory |

