.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
House: craftsman, cottage, modern
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, lawyer
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, mah-jongg
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, spy, adventure
1. the modern house is on the far left##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
6. the bartender is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| House          | modern     | cottage    | craftsman    |
| Job         | bartender | lawyer | freelancer     |
| Game   | snooker  | whist      | mah-jongg        |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero   | spy   | adventure |

 